videos.description: Oklahoma State's Cameron McGriff has the alley-oop dunk off a Jeffrey Carrol pass.
videos.headline: McGriff finishes the alley-oop pass with a slam

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Mitchell Solomon gets a block which results in Phil Forte III making 3-Pointer at the other end.
videos.headline: Oklahoma State takes their first lead of the game

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Cameron McGriff takes advantage of a clear path to the basket with a dunk.
videos.headline: McGriff drives in for the open dunk

videos.description: Oklahoma State's Jawun Evans finds Jeffrey Carroll along the baseline for a 2-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Carroll cuts to the basket for a powerful 2-handed slam

videos.description: Iowa State's Monte Morris knocks down a 3-Pointer to give Iowa State a 70-69 lead.
videos.headline: Iowa State reclaims the lead

videos.description: Iowa State's Monte Morris makes a second straight 3-pointer to give Iowa State a 73-69 lead.
videos.headline: Morris hits another 3-Pointer to extend Iowa State lead

videos.description: Breaking down Monte Morris and Phil Forte III's performances in Iowa State's 96-86 win against Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Postgame Breakdown of Iowa State's 96-86 victory over Oklahoma State
